      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Monster Maniacs",
        "Client": "Lovely \u2606 Idol",
        "Description": "I\u2019ve met some crazy fans before,\r\nbut these guys are foaming at the\r\nmouth to get an autograph! I know\r\nit\u2019s hard to resist my charm, but\r\nI need security to get rid of them,\r\npronto. When they\u0027re gone, I\u2019ll teach\r\nyou some super cutesy poses!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Volvidon, an Anjanath\r\nand a Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Des fans monstrueux",
        "Client": "Idol \u2606 adorable",
        "Description": "C\u0027est pas la premi\u00E8re fois que je\r\nvois des fans d\u00E9chain\u00E9s, mais ceux-l\u00E0\r\n\u00E9cument carr\u00E9ment pour un autographe !\r\nJe sais bien que je suis irr\u00E9sistible,\r\nmais j\u0027appr\u00E9cierais si tu pouvais\r\ncalmer leurs ardeurs. En \u00E9change, je\r\nt\u0027apprendrai des poses trop choupi !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Volvidon, un Anjanath\r\net un Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Ossessione mostruosa",
        "Client": "Idolo \u2606 adorabile",
        "Description": "Ho gi\u00E0 incontrato fan scatenati,\r\nma questi schiumano di rabbia\r\nper un autografo! So che sono\r\nirresistibile, ma gli addetti alla\r\nsicurezza devono liberarsene\r\nsubito. Una volta eliminati, ti\r\ninsegner\u00F2 delle mosse adorabili!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Volvidon, un Anjanath\r\ne un Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Monsterfanatiker",
        "Client": "Liebliches \u2606 Idol",
        "Description": "Bin rabiate Fans gewohnt, aber\r\ndiese holen sich das Autogramm\r\nmit Gewalt! Ich brauche sofort\r\neinen Bodyguard, um sie loszu-\r\nwerden. Wenn sie weg sind,\r\nzeige ich dir niedliche Posen!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Volvidon, einen Anjanath\r\nund einen Tigrex.",
